include ../mixins/container

mixin TestTheirLoyalty(values)
  +container(values)
    p When <strong>your conditional companionâ€™s loyalty is at its minimum (0)</strong>, you can attempt to convince them to stay by your side. If you do, roll +heart. If the companion is a hireling, roll +wealth instead. Add +2 if you share a bond. If their goal is lost to you, count this move as a miss.
    p On a <strong>strong hit</strong>, your companion stands by your side. Give +you heart+1 to their loyalty. Take +1 momentum.
